{"UNSLACKED":[{"def":"Not slacked; unslaked; as, unslacked lime.","pos":""}],"UNSLAKED":[{"def":"Not slaked; unslacked; as, an unslaked thirst; unslaked lime.","pos":""}],"UNSLING":[{"def":"To take off the slings of, as a yard, a cask, or the like; to release from the slings.","pos":""}],"UNSLUICE":[{"def":"To sluice; to open the sluice or sluices of; to let flow; to discharge.","pos":""}]}